      "text": "Complete tone summary"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "The \"String Theory\" that we have learnt in this book are the essential rules for tone production, and for 99% of words you will not need to remember anything else but those. However, if you're a perfectionist and want to know all there is to know about tone rules, including those that are hardly used ones, here are all the possible combinations."
    },
